author: Telegraph Sport
title: Wayne Rooney confirms he will stay at Manchester United
text:
Wayne Rooney confirms he will stay at Manchester United Wayne Rooney is staying at Old Trafford Credit: pa  33pm 
W ayne Rooney has announced he is staying at Manchester United. Who is your clubs all-time leading goalscorer? 
T he statement read: "Despite the interest which has been shown from other clubs, for which I'm grateful, I want to end recent speculation and say that I am staying at Manchester United. 
"I hope I will play a full part in helping the team in its fight for success on four fronts. 
"It's an exciting time at the club and I want to remain a part of it."
